  "description": "The coupling preset: Full Column Low. OCEANDEEP holds the bottom of the water column — filterCutoff=700, the shallow end of the darkness filter, maximum transparency. bodyChar=0 (Open Water): no coloration, no room, just the column. This pairs with OPENSKY at the surface. Together they describe the complete vertical range of existence.",
