    "revelation": null,
    "god": null,
    "flock_note": "Designed to pair with an OPENSKY preset. filterCutoff=700 is as high as OCEANDEEP goes — approaching the surface without breaking through. subLevel=0.5 leaves room for OPENSKY to occupy the upper register. The PRESSURE macro can gradually separate the two engines by adding compression.",
